{{template "head" .}}

{{template "navbar" .}}

<div class="weather-container">
    <h1 class="text-purple">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="card margin-y-lg">
        <h2 class="text-cyan">Data Collection</h2>
        <p>We collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Email address, username, and password (hashed) when you create an account</li>
            <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> Locations you save for weather tracking</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Access logs, API usage, and feature interactions</li>
            <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, device information</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card margin-y-lg">
        <h2 class="text-cyan">How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <p>Your data is used for:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Providing weather information for your saved locations</li>
            <li>Sending weather alerts and notifications</li>
            <li>Improving service quality and user experience</li>
            <li>Security monitoring and abuse prevention</li>
            <li>Technical support and troubleshooting</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card margin-y-lg">
        <h2 class="text-cyan">Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain your data as follows:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Account Data:</strong> Until you delete your account</li>
            <li><strong>Access Logs:</strong> 7 days (configurable by administrator)</li>
            <li><strong>Audit Logs:</strong> 90 days minimum for security purposes</li>
            <li><strong>Weather Data:</strong> Cached temporarily (typically 10-60 minutes)</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card margin-y-lg">
        <h2 class="text-cyan">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Open-Meteo:</strong> Weather data provider</li>
            <li><strong>USGS:</strong> Earthquake data</li>
            <li><strong>GeoIP Databases:</strong> Location detection (IP-based)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not share your personal information with these services. API requests are anonymous.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card margin-y-lg">
        <h2 class="text-cyan">Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use the following cookies:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Session Cookie:</strong> Required for authentication and login persistence</li>
            <li><strong>CSRF Token:</strong> Required for security (form submission protection)</li>
            <li><strong>Preferences:</strong> Optional - stores your theme and display preferences</li>
        </ul>
        <p>All cookies are first-party only. We do not use third-party tracking cookies.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card margin-y-lg">
        <h2 class="text-cyan">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Access:</strong> View all data we have about you</li>
            <li><strong>Export:</strong> Download your data in machine-readable format</li>
            <li><strong>Modify:</strong> Update your account information and preferences</li>
            <li><strong>Delete:</strong> Permanently delete your account and all associated data</li>
            <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> Disable notifications and alerts</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Access these features from your <a href="/user/profile" class="text-cyan">profile page</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card margin-y-lg">
        <h2 class="text-cyan">Security</h2>
        <p>We protect your data using:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Encrypted connections (HTTPS/TLS)</li>
            <li>Bcrypt password hashing</li>
            <li>CSRF protection on all forms</li>
            <li>Rate limiting to prevent abuse</li>
            <li>Regular security audits</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card margin-y-lg">
        <h2 class="text-cyan">Contact</h2>
        <p>For privacy concerns or data requests, please contact us:</p>
        <div class="margin-y-md">
            <a href="/server/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Form</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card margin-y-lg">
        <p class="text-comment"><small>Last updated: {{.server.BuildDate}}</small></p>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
// Initialize notification polling
if (typeof Notifications !== 'undefined') {
    Notifications.startPolling(30000);
}
</script>

